{{> header title=(concat "Your " brand.displayName " nbn® HFC order")}}

<tr>
  <td style="padding: 20px 15px;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>Order number:</strong> %%ORDER_NUMBER%%
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Hi %%NAME%%,
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          It's great to have you on board with {{brand.displayName}} nbn®. Here are the next steps to get you set up and connected to the internet.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Your plan and service</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>Your plan is the:</strong> %%PLAN%%<br />%%STATIC_IP_CALCULATION%%
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Here are various other important documents relating to your nbn® service:
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <a href="%%CRITICAL_INFORMATION_SUMMARY_CIS%%" style="color: {{brand.colors.primary}}; text-decoration: underline;">Critical Information Summary (CIS)</a><br /><a href="%%KEY_FACT_SHEET%%" style="color: {{brand.colors.primary}}; text-decoration: underline;">Key Fact Sheet</a><br />
          <a href="%%TERMS_NAME%%" style="color: {{brand.colors.primary}}; text-decoration: underline;">Terms and Conditions</a></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Technology Type</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <strong>Your nbn® technology type is:</strong> Hybrid Fibre Coaxial (HFC)
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          For more information on your technology type and what’s required for installation, check out our <a href="%%SUPPORT_PAGE%%" style="color: {{brand.colors.primary}}; text-decoration: underline;">support page</a>.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Modem</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          You can plug in your {{brand.displayName}} modem using our <a href="%%SETUP_GUIDE%%" style="color: {{brand.colors.primary}}; text-decoration: underline;">setup guide</a>.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          If you’re using your own modem, check out our <a href="%%BYO_SETUP_GUIDE%%" style="color: {{brand.colors.primary}}; text-decoration: underline;">BYO setup guide</a>.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; color: {{brand.colors.headerText}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">
          <strong>Installation Details</strong>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          To install your service, nbn® will send you a Connection Box with instructions on how to connect it to your modem. We’ll email you a tracking number for the delivery.
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
            <li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">You’ll need both the nbn® Connection Box and your modem to get online.</li>
            <li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">Someone 18 years or older will need to set up the devices.</li>
            <li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">If you aren’t the owner of the property, you’ll also need permission from the owner or strata manager for installation.</li>
            <li style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 8px;">Please note that any {{brand.displayName}} modem will be sent in a separate delivery.</li>
          </ul>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}}; padding-bottom: 20px;">
          Should you have a question about your order, please call us on {{brand.support.phone}} and we’ll be happy to help.
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td style="padding: 20px 15px 60px;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: {{brand.colors.text}};">
          Thanks,<br>
          Your {{brand.displayName}} Team
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td>
</tr>

{{> footer showThingsHeading=true showNbnTrademark=true}}
